headline: Northern Trust Selected by Mereo Insurance to Provide Asset Servicing and Asset Management Solutions
summary: CHICAGO, June 17, 2025--In addition to providing custody services and institutional brokerage solutions, Northern Trust will manage part of Mereo’s fixed income portfolio.
